# Commit Discipline

- Use tagged commit messages like `[FIX]`, `[LEARN]`, `[DOCS]`, `[TEST]`, `[INFRA]`.
- Keep one concern per commit.
- Run the repo verification command before committing when configured.
- Do not introduce repo-defined forbidden patterns.
- If a commit changes a benchmark or score, include the measured number in the message.
